title: High-Speed Processing Boards for Demanding Naval Applications
text:
High-Speed Processing Boards for Demanding Naval Applications 01 September 2015 by ISPAS 
ISPAS supplies high-speed motherboards for signal and radar processing systems. 
These specialised, high-tech boards are designed to excel in the next-generation of compact, high-performance signal processing systems. 
Please download the free paper for more information about how these motherboards can benefit naval applications such as image processing, sonar and ultrasound. Available Downloads
